Running command: python - <<'PY'
import requests
for url in [
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/openapi.json',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/openapi.yaml',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/docs',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/redoc',
]:
    r=requests.get(url, timeout=10)
    print(url, r.status_code, r.headers.get('content-type'))
    print(r.text[:120].replace('\n',' '))
